/hpc2hdd/home/xhao390/py/urbanclip/data/: The image captures a panoramic view of a street in Beijing, China. The perspective is from a car on the road, giving a driver's eye view of the scene. The street is lined with lush green trees and bushes, providing a vibrant contrast to the clear blue sky above. Power lines stretch across the sky, adding a touch of urbanity to the otherwise natural landscape. Cars can be seen driving down the road, adding a sense of motion and life to the scene. The image is taken from a low angle, which emphasizes the height of the trees and the vastness of the sky. The colors in the image are bright and vibrant, enhancing the overall visual appeal.
